WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.316
The pathologic cascade proceeds in four

00:00:03.316 --> 00:00:03.868
steps.

00:00:03.868 --> 00:00:07.184
Direct viral injury or immune-mediated attack

00:00:07.184 --> 00:00:10.500
triggers T-cell infiltration and a cytokine

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:11.053
surge.

00:00:11.053 --> 00:00:13.263
Myocyte necrosis releases troponin.

00:00:13.263 --> 00:00:16.579
Edema, fibrosis, and impaired contractility produce

00:00:16.579 --> 00:00:19.895
the ventricular dysfunction that underlies every

00:00:19.895 --> 00:00:21.000
downstream complication.
